*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZPRG_SAMPLE_SUB_PARA
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT ZPRG_SAMPLE_SUB_PARA.

DATA : lo TYPE numc3.
PARAMETERS : lv1 TYPE numc3.
PARAMETERS : lv2 TYPE numc3.
PERFORM sum USING lv1 lv2 CHANGING lo.
WRITE lo.
*INCLUDE yg_sample_sub_para_sumf01.
FORM sum USING lv1 lv2 CHANGING lo.
  lo = lv1 + lv2.
ENDFORM.
